text.textblock: In the Matter of Certain Plastic Encapsulated Integrated Circuits: Designation of Commission Investigative Attorney

Notice is hereby given that, as of this date, Thomas L. Jarvis, Esq. of the Office of Unfair Import Investigations is designated as the Commission investigative attorney in the above-cited investigation.
The Secretary is requested to publish this Notice in the
